data.description: YOUR NEW HOME AWAITS IN BRITTANY LAKES! THIS SPACIOUS, UPDATED HOME SITS ON AN OVER-SIZED LOT ON A PRIVATE CUL-DE-SAC STREET. INSIDE YOU WILL FIND STYLISH COLUMNS, HIGH CEILINGS, AND BEAUTIFUL PORCELAIN WOOD TILE FLOORING.OPEN CONCEPT FLOOR PLAN INCLUDES FORMAL DINING, FORMAL LIVING, STUDY, AND A LARGE KITCHEN WHERE YOU WILL FIND A BREAKFAST BAR, CUSTOM-MADE 53" WOODEN CABINETS, GRANITE COUNTERTOPS, SUBWAY-TILE BACKSPLASH, WALK-IN PANTRY, AND A GAS RANGE. THE LARGE PRIMARY BEDROOM FEATURES AN UPDATED EN SUITE BATH WITH A JETTED TUB, SEPARATE SHOWER AND LARGE WALK-IN CLOSET. MASSIVE BACKYARD HAS PLENTY OF SPACE FOR THE POOL OF YOUR DREAMS. LOCATED IN THE HIGHLY-RATED CCISD, THE PROPERTY TAX RATE HERE IS REMARKABLY LOW. GREAT COMMUNITY WITH POOL, TENNIS COURTS, AND WELL-MAINTAINED PARKS AND GROUNDS. DONT DELAY, MAKE YOUR SHOWING APPOINTMENT TODAY!
